				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Karlach's inparty dialogue when she's in your party and you click on her\r\nOrder of nodes:\r\n1. Generic Blockers (Jaheira/Other avatar/Mindflayer)\r\n2. IPRDs (will override anything under it)\r\n3. Astarion's bite\r\n4. InRegion/specific situations branches\r\n5. Romance branches.\r\n6. Default greeting node."
